  <brief_title>Can Alternative Treatment Have an Impact on Cervical Dysplasia?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Mindfulness Meditation Limit the Progression and/or Increase the Remission of Cervical Dysplasia?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
